 liqueur, stir it in with the raspberries.\n\n5. Layer the fool in individual serving glasses: alternate layers of\n   white chocolate cream with raspberry mixture, ending with a swirl\n   of cream on top.\n\n6. Chill for at least 1 hour. Just before serving, top with reserved\n   fresh raspberries and a small mint leaf.\n\nSERVING SUGGESTION: Pair with buttery shortbread biscuits or ladyfinger cookies.\nA dessert wine like Moscato d'Asti complements beautifully.","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
